## Metrics

| Metric | Locked definition | Note |
|---|---|---|
| CAC | {{Blended: total S&M spend ÷ new customers in period | Paid-only: paid-channel spend ÷ paid-channel customers in period}} | Use locked variant throughout |
| LTV | {{e.g., Gross margin × ACV × (1/churn rate), using observed M+12 churn}} | |
| ARR | {{e.g., MRR × 12, where MRR is current-month subscription revenue}} | Not forward-looking |
| Cohort retention | {{Logo retention at fixed intervals (M+1, M+3, M+6, M+12)}} | Distinct from revenue retention |
| Gross burn | Total monthly cash outflow | |
| Net burn | Gross burn minus revenue and other inflow | |
| Runway | Current cash ÷ trailing-3-month net burn avg | Always net |

